These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, musical, thriller
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, motorbike, roller
1. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
2. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
3. the person driving the car is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
5. the person driving the roller is between the person driving the car and the person driving the motorbike##2
6. the person watching thriller movies is the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | crime     | musical | disaster |
| Transport     | bike     | motorbike | roller  | car      |

