.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, collecting, dancing, fishing
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, brazilian, egyptian, indian
1. the indian is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the egyptian##2
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
4. the egyptian is on the left or right of the indian##3
5. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
6. the argentine is on the right of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | collecting | board-games | fishing | dancing  |
| Nationality   | brazilian  | argentine   | indian  | egyptian |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, hot-chocolate, soy-milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, hiking, singing, woodworking
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
4. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | 7up    | fanta   | hot-chocolate | soy-milk    |
| Hobby      | hiking | drawing | singing       | woodworking |

