.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, juice, soy-milk
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, roller, train, tram
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
2. the person driving the train is between the person driving the tram and the person drinking juice##2
3. the person driving the boat is between the person driving the train and the person drinking coffee##2
4. the person driving the tram is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | coffee | juice | soy-milk | fanta |
| Transport   | roller | boat  | train    | tram  |

