4. the indian is between the french and the thai##2
5. the person driving the ship is the person driving the ship##1
6. the person driving the ship is between the person driving the snowmobile and the thai##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2   |   3    |     4      |
| Nationality   | egyptian | thai | indian | french     |
| Transport     | airplane | van  | ship   | snowmobile |

