2. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
5. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
6. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Hobby         | fishing | filmmaking | board-games | drawing   |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | scientific | horror      | superhero |

