2. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is the owner of the snake##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left or far right##3
6. the owner of the fish is between the person who's sport is skiing and the person who's sport is basketball##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Pet     | chinchilla | fish   | horse      | snake      |
| Sport   | skiing     | tennis | basketball | volleyball |

