.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, electronic, jazz, salsa
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, chinese, nigerian, russian
1. the argentine is on the right of the chinese##1
2. the fan of jazz is between the russian and the chinese##2
3. the fan of electronic is the chinese##1
4. the nigerian is on the left of the chinese##1
5. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the argentine##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | classical | electronic | jazz      | salsa   |
| Nationality   | nigerian  | chinese    | argentine | russian |

