3. the person driving the tram is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
5. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
6. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby       | card-games | filmmaking | writing    | chess      |
| Transport   | taxi       | tram       | snowmobile | skateboard |

