.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-13::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, canadian, german, turkish
4 different pets are kept: bird, fish, frog, hamster
1. the canadian is on the far right##1
2. the american is the american##1
3. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
4. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the canadian##3
5. the german is on the left or right of the turkish##3
6. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the turkish##3
7. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Nationality   | american | german  | turkish | canadian |
| Pet           | frog     | hamster | bird    | fish     |

