.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-14::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, cabbage, plum, potato
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, librarian, manager, musician
1. the person eating potato is on the left or right of the librarian##3
2. the librarian is on the right of the manager##1
3. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the bartender##1
4. the librarian is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating plum is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Food   | cabbage  | artichoke | potato  | plum      |
| Job    | musician | bartender | manager | librarian |

