.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, collecting, dancing, rock-climbing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, indie, metal, techno
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far right##1
2. the fan of indie is on the left of the fan of metal##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is the fan of techno##1
4. the fan of indie is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
5. the fan of metal is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
6. the fan of metal is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
7. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | collecting | rock-climbing | dancing | card-games |
| Music-Genre   | techno     | dubstep       | indie   | metal      |

